tury, and has been especially popular in Scotland.  See also  Annis ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Agnes Badwell was born in 1452. She married Richard Knapp. She died in 1498, in Barking, Suffolk, England, United Kingdom, at the age of 46."},"et":{"1452–1498":"1452–1498","1450–1527":"1450–1527","1464–1527":"1464–1527","1473–Male":"1473–Surnud","–1540":"–1540","1498":"1498","1464":"1464","1452":"1452","1540":"1540","1473":"1473","1450":"1450","1527":"1527","Barking, Suffolk, England":"Barking, Suffolk, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1452–1498":"1452–1498","1450–1527":"1450–1527","1464–1527":"1464–1527","1473–Male":"1473–Kuollut","–1540":"–1540","1498":"1498","1464":"1464","1452":"1452","1540":"1540","1473":"1473","1450":"1450","1527":"1527","Barking, Suffolk, England":"Barking, Suffolk, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1452–1498":"1452–1498","1450–1527":"1450–1527","1464–1527":"1464–1527","1473–Male":"1473–Décédé","–1540":"–1540","1498":"1498","1464":"1464","1452":"1452","1540":"1540","1473":"1473","1450":"1450","1527":"1527","Barking, Suffolk, England":"Barking, Suffolk, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Agnes Badwell est née en 1452. Elle a épousé Richard Knapp. Elle est décédée en 1498, à Barking, Suffolk, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni, à l’âge de 46 ans."},"de":{"1452–1498":"1452–1498","1450–1527":"1450–1527","1464–1527":"1464–1527","1473–Male":"1473–Verstorben","–1540":"–1540","1498":"1498","1464":"1464","1452":"1452","1540":"1540","1473":"1473","1450":"1450","1527":"1527","Barking, Suffolk, England":"Barking, Suffolk, England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Agnes Badwell wurde 1452 geboren. Sie hat Richard Knapp geheiratet. Sie starb 1498 im Alter von 46 Jahren in Barking, Suffolk, England, United Kingdom."},"ht":{"1452–1498":"1452–1498","1450–1527":"1450–1527","1464–1527":"1464–1527","1473–Male":"1473–Desede","–1540":"–1540","1498":"1498","1464":"1464","1452":"1452","1540":"1540","1473":"1473","1450":"1450","1527":"1527","Barking, Suffolk, E